# Project Overview

This is a development workspace following modern TypeScript/JavaScript practices with comprehensive rules for code quality, commits, and architecture patterns.

## Key Principles
- Follow atomic development practices
- Maintain clean, descriptive code
- Use proper TypeScript typing
- Follow conventional commit standards

**Note**: Specific rules for different file types and contexts are defined in the `/rules/` directory and will be automatically applied based on file patterns and context.
